    "It can be seen from the figure that words such as \"localization\" and \"recognition\" are hot topics for temporal action detection.",
    "Keywords such as \"human action recognition\" and \"temporal action proposal generation\" are also the focus of this paper.",
    "The keywords in Fig. 8 complement each other and make up for the ambiguity of the time information in Fig.",
    "Through these keywords, readers can better understand the hotspot direction in respect of TAD.",
    "With the development of deep learning, increasing numbers of scholars and teams have begun to study TAD, and they jointly promote the progress and development of TAD algorithms."
